                    <img src="{{ cdn_url }}/images/home/press-images/g@2x.png" alt="The Guardian - Why Facebook and Microsoft say chatbots are the talk of the town"></img>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-2">
                <a href="https://www.ft.com/content/6755beb8-320c-11e6-bda0-04585c31b153" target="_blank">
                    <img src="{{ cdn_url }}/images/home/press-images/ft@2x.png" alt="Financial Times - Innovation to watch: Friends based insurance"></img>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-2">
                <a href="http://www.postonline.co.uk/post/news/2466996/so-sure-prepares-to-launch-revolutionary-insurance-model" target="_blank">
                    <img src="{{ cdn_url }}/images/home/press-images/ip@2x.png" alt="Insurance Post - so-sure to launch revolutionary social peer-to-peer mobile insurance app"></img>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-2">
                <h5 style="text-transform: uppercase">
                    Awarded by
                </h5>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-2">
                <a href="http://www.postevents.co.uk/technologyawards/static/shortlist-1" target="_blank">
                    <img src="{{ cdn_url }}/images/home/press-images/di@2x.png" alt="Post Digital Insurance Awards 2016 - so-sure nominated for The New Kid on the Block Award"></img>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="pre-footer">
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-a">
        <h4>
            <a href="https://help.wearesosure.com/hc/en-us/categories/200913949-How-it-Works" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
        </h4>
        <p>Learn more about how Social Insurance works and why you should join us. We also cover all the basics to help you understand exactly what you're paying for.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-6 col-b">
        <h4>
            <a href="https://wearesosure.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/207523059-Our-mission">Our Mission</a>
        </h4>
        <p>Insurance is rubbish. We're making it better by returning it to
            <a href="https://blog.wearesosure.com/how-insurance-works-ccba082dcbe#.r4cj6kbnw" target="_blank">how it all started</a>. We call this Social Insurance. Starting with mobile phones, then the world!</p>
    </div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="modal modal-switching fade" id="switchingModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
        <h2 class="modal-title">Want to switch to so-sure?</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body modal-switching-body">
        <h4>Switching to so-sure is easy. Just follow these steps:</h4>
        <ol>
            <li>Contact your existing insurance provider and request to cancel your policy. Check on their website but often you can email them and, at most, give them a 30 day notice.
            </li>
            <li>
                Download the so-sure app and purchase your new policy from so-sure.
            </li>
        </ol>
        <p class="text-center">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">Got it!</button>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

